Planned for Version 1.1
* performance report (done)
* add some small annotations like arrows, bullets and some text markers (done)
* implement automatic, scriptable TradingSystems (work in progress)
* implement scriptable TradingSystem Simulations (work in progress)
* Maven2 support based on the work of Udo KÃ¼hne

Planned for Version 1.2
* calculate price of the certificate correctly in case underlying is in USD/GPB/JPY
* support of more warrants (KO, discount, plain vanilla put/call, bonus) and shares
* support for additional warrants and issuers (Commerzbank, Paribas, Vontobel, L&S, Trinkhaus etc.)
* additional EOD-quotes for the past 5 years
* information of financial figures and balance sheet data
* backtesting and simulation module

Planned for version 1.4
* support for additional brokers (IB, ...)


